WEBVTT

01:35.000 --> 01:37.720
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL OF THE SAME NAME
BY ZHU YI ON WWW.JJWXC.NET

01:37.800 --> 01:38.800
BEIYU, OFFICER CHEN'S HOME

01:38.880 --> 01:40.000
My house is a bit small.

01:40.080 --> 01:41.280
Hope you like it.

01:41.360 --> 01:42.440
Come in.

01:42.520 --> 01:45.160
Mom. Why are you back so late?

01:45.240 --> 01:47.240
I'm starving!

01:47.960 --> 01:48.920
Who is she?

01:49.000 --> 01:50.440
Let me introduce a new friend to you.

01:50.520 --> 01:52.200
She'll be staying with us for a while.

01:52.280 --> 01:54.160
Give me a hug! Welcome to our home!

01:54.240 --> 01:55.680
Be gentle. Don't be so reckless.

01:55.760 --> 01:56.960
I'm sorry.

01:57.040 --> 01:59.080
Do you want to try this?
It's super delicious!

01:59.160 --> 02:00.800
I've already eaten. Sorry.

02:01.720 --> 02:02.840
If there's anything
you want to eat or drink,

02:02.920 --> 02:04.720
- just tell Xi.
- It's really good!

02:04.800 --> 02:06.240
- I'm not hungry, thanks.
- Just try a little.

02:09.360 --> 02:10.759
Let me show you our secret base.

02:17.040 --> 02:18.520
This is our secret base!

02:18.600 --> 02:19.800
What do you think?

02:19.880 --> 02:23.160
We can read here
and talk about our secrets.

02:23.240 --> 02:24.760
Or even play games.

02:24.840 --> 02:25.880
Do you like it?

02:26.440 --> 02:27.280
Come.

02:28.320 --> 02:29.640
This is my mom's room.

02:29.720 --> 02:31.080
Just ignore it.

02:31.160 --> 02:32.400
Come in. And this.

02:32.480 --> 02:33.400
This is my bedroom.

02:33.920 --> 02:35.920
Come in. Let me show you something.

02:37.080 --> 02:37.920
Isn't it awesome?

02:38.000 --> 02:40.640
Warm in winter, and cool in summer.

02:40.720 --> 02:43.120
We can squeeze in however we like.

02:44.440 --> 02:47.000
Oh, do you play games?

02:47.600 --> 02:49.160
I think you look like

02:49.240 --> 02:51.440
that Bone Spirit
from Fantasy Westward Journey.

02:51.520 --> 02:52.360
Seriously, you really do!

02:52.440 --> 02:54.960
But I think you're prettier than her.
What happened to your eyes?

02:55.040 --> 02:56.480
Xi, Yifan!

02:56.560 --> 02:57.520
Come eat!

02:57.600 --> 02:59.480
Coming! Let's go. Time to eat.

02:59.560 --> 03:01.240
Alright, the food's ready.

03:01.320 --> 03:03.600
Why did you make such a feast
just because Yifan's here?

03:04.200 --> 03:06.040
Do I usually starve you or what?

03:06.640 --> 03:08.560
Dig in, Yifan. Make yourself at home.

03:10.040 --> 03:11.080
Oh, right, Yifan.

03:11.160 --> 03:13.080
My name is Chen Xi.
The "Xi" means "cherish".

03:13.160 --> 03:14.640
Doesn't it sound a bit old-fashioned?

03:15.200 --> 03:16.760
I used to really want to change it.

03:16.840 --> 03:18.560
But my mom told me
I should learn to cherish things.

03:19.160 --> 03:21.160
And I was like, cherish what exactly?

03:21.920 --> 03:23.520
Until I met you guys.

03:24.880 --> 03:25.720
We?

03:27.960 --> 03:30.920
Actually, you're not
the first girl to stay at our house.

03:31.000 --> 03:33.880
Before you came,
other girls stayed here, too.

03:33.960 --> 03:36.480
At first, they weren't very happy.

03:36.560 --> 03:42.240
But ever since they came
to our house, all the girls

03:42.320 --> 03:43.480
became so much happier.

03:43.560 --> 03:45.360
So, Yifan,

03:45.440 --> 03:46.480
you have to trust me.

03:46.560 --> 03:49.280
As long as I'm here, I'll make sure

03:49.360 --> 03:50.800
you're happy and cheerful.

03:51.400 --> 03:53.280
Alright. Why do you talk
so much while eating?

03:53.880 --> 03:56.040
Finish your meal first.
You'll have plenty of time to chat later.

03:56.680 --> 03:58.680
- Okay.
- Yifan, eat more.

04:00.640 --> 04:02.560
Mom, what time is it now?

04:02.640 --> 04:04.200
Are you serious? Can't you check yourself?

04:05.840 --> 04:07.840
I have something to do. Take your time.

04:07.920 --> 04:09.880
- Where are you going?
- Yifan, eat more.

04:09.960 --> 04:11.240
I need to change my university preference.

04:11.320 --> 04:13.160
Can't you do that after eating?

04:17.320 --> 04:18.399
Submitted!

04:21.519 --> 04:24.320
Now, I can go to the same university
as my idol!

04:27.120 --> 04:28.960
Can I borrow your computer?

04:29.040 --> 04:30.640
Sure. Go ahead.

04:32.520 --> 04:33.560
Take a seat.

04:34.360 --> 04:36.520
What are you going to do? Need my help?

04:38.160 --> 04:39.120
I want to change my preference.

04:39.800 --> 04:41.080
You have an idol, too?

04:42.960 --> 04:45.480
I just want to leave
everyone I know behind

04:47.040 --> 04:48.880
and go somewhere no one knows me.

04:50.600 --> 04:51.640
That's all.

04:56.160 --> 04:58.520
Yifan, don't be scared.

04:59.560 --> 05:01.920
Just finish changing it first.
I'll leave you to it.

05:20.840 --> 05:21.920
3,834 DAYS

05:24.120 --> 05:27.120
Boss, sure you don't need
to go to hospital?

05:28.520 --> 05:29.360
No need.

05:30.440 --> 05:33.000
Boss, why did you hit him yourself?

05:33.080 --> 05:34.160
We could've just called the police.

05:35.520 --> 05:37.520
He is in a bad mood lately. Stop talking.

05:38.120 --> 05:39.440
I already said no.

05:40.160 --> 05:41.040
Are we doing business or not?

05:42.120 --> 05:43.520
Let's go.

06:01.920 --> 06:03.360
What a fight.

06:03.440 --> 06:04.560
There's a long cut

06:05.400 --> 06:07.120
on our boss's face.

06:07.640 --> 06:08.640
Yet he refused to go to hospital.

06:09.560 --> 06:10.480
He just treated it himself.

06:11.760 --> 06:12.800
Boss is here.

06:16.400 --> 06:17.600
They know each other?

06:25.920 --> 06:28.160
- You got hurt?
- None of your business.

06:29.040 --> 06:29.920
Why are you here?

06:32.920 --> 06:34.400
What exactly happened
between you and Dian?

06:37.680 --> 06:38.720
I want to know that, too.

06:38.800 --> 06:40.800
You drove her away,

06:41.840 --> 06:43.000
and now act like you know nothing.

06:46.920 --> 06:48.720
I've been searching for her
for six months.

06:50.760 --> 06:52.960
During these six months,
I never thought about giving up.

06:58.240 --> 07:00.440
She might be in Hong Kong, China.

07:02.520 --> 07:03.400
How do you know?

07:07.520 --> 07:09.080
Dear passengers,

07:09.160 --> 07:12.560
we regret to inform you that Flight R1307

07:12.640 --> 07:15.560
is delayed due to weather conditions.

07:15.640 --> 07:18.160
Please check for updates
at the boarding gate.

07:18.240 --> 07:19.720
Thank you for your understanding.

07:19.800 --> 07:21.280
I don't want to see her
living like this either.

07:22.160 --> 07:23.680
If there's any misunderstanding
between you two,

07:23.760 --> 07:26.360
- maybe I can help clear it up.
- There is no misunderstanding.

07:26.440 --> 07:27.720
But I heard

07:27.800 --> 07:29.640
you've always minded
the fact that she disappeared

07:29.720 --> 07:30.560
after the college entrance exam.

07:33.520 --> 07:35.440
What I said before
about her and I planning

07:35.520 --> 07:38.640
to go to Yihe University together
was nonsense.

07:39.840 --> 07:41.960
I made it up just to mess with you.

07:42.960 --> 07:44.080
But you didn't react,

07:44.800 --> 07:45.640
so I thought you didn't care.

07:46.240 --> 07:47.400
Then why did she suddenly
apply to Yihe University?

07:48.520 --> 07:49.800
I don't know either.

07:54.520 --> 07:57.160
AIR CHINA

07:58.480 --> 08:01.240
But if I had to guess,
it might have something to do

08:01.320 --> 08:04.240
with her uncle's family.

08:04.320 --> 08:06.200
I know she had a hard time back then.

08:07.080 --> 08:09.600
I also heard her aunt yelling at her.

08:10.440 --> 08:11.880
And it wasn't just her aunt.

08:12.880 --> 08:15.720
There was also some…
some Uncle Che of hers.

08:16.880 --> 08:18.320
She never told us about it.

08:18.400 --> 08:20.840
But one time, when Qiao
was on the phone with Dian,

08:20.920 --> 08:22.240
Qiao overheard it.

08:23.040 --> 08:24.200
She said there was someone

08:24.760 --> 08:26.320
who called himself Uncle Che.

08:27.200 --> 08:29.320
He said a lot of strange things to Dian.

08:30.120 --> 08:33.440
After that summer
after the college entrance exam,

08:33.960 --> 08:36.919
Dian moved away.
No one knew where she went.

08:43.360 --> 08:44.200
Where is she now?

08:44.280 --> 08:46.160
I think I saw her at the Star Ferry Pier
in Hong Kong, China.

08:47.000 --> 08:48.840
I called out to her,
but she didn't respond.

08:49.360 --> 08:51.280
Then I followed her.
She ran into a building.

08:51.360 --> 08:53.320
I searched for days after that
but found nothing.

08:55.040 --> 08:57.600
Can you give me the name
and address of that building?

08:58.560 --> 08:59.840
- Sure.
- Thanks.

09:00.640 --> 09:02.600
But I'm really not sure if that was her.

09:02.680 --> 09:06.440
Flight R1307 is now boarding.

09:08.080 --> 09:14.520
HONG KONG, CHINA

09:19.840 --> 09:22.200
Wen Yifan? There's no such person here.

09:22.920 --> 09:24.360
Could you check again?

09:25.040 --> 09:27.760
I told you, no such person here.

09:33.720 --> 09:36.840
But can you describe her for me?

09:36.920 --> 09:37.880
Wait a moment.

09:39.600 --> 09:40.440
Here, look.

09:43.240 --> 09:44.440
I see.

09:46.360 --> 09:48.760
But as far as I remember,
her surname isn't Wen.

09:50.000 --> 09:51.120
Not Wen?

09:51.680 --> 09:54.080
Look. She registered
under the surname Sang.

09:54.160 --> 09:55.040
She already moved out.

10:03.720 --> 10:04.560
Thanks.

10:07.160 --> 10:08.400
She was so beautiful.

10:08.480 --> 10:10.240
Of course, I remember her.

10:10.320 --> 10:13.320
But she always looked like
she had a lot on her mind.

10:13.400 --> 10:15.720
She seemed really unhappy.

10:16.400 --> 10:17.440
Every day,

10:17.520 --> 10:19.880
she just ate bread and bottled water.

10:19.960 --> 10:21.320
That was her whole meal.

10:22.560 --> 10:23.600
I have no idea

10:23.680 --> 10:24.840
why she was living like that.

10:45.760 --> 10:47.800
BING'S TEA HOUSE

10:48.720 --> 10:50.000
Why are you showing up this late?

10:50.080 --> 10:51.320
Sorry, I'm late.

10:52.080 --> 10:54.280
There's a lot to do!

11:01.520 --> 11:03.880
Yan, you don't even know if Wen Yifan

11:03.960 --> 11:05.600
is in Hong Kong, China.

11:06.480 --> 11:07.880
Why don't you come back to Nanwu first?

11:08.560 --> 11:09.920
How are you going
to find her in such a huge city?

11:11.200 --> 11:12.280
Besides,

11:12.800 --> 11:14.520
doesn't your department
have a new project to launch?

11:15.480 --> 11:17.160
The marketing team is waiting on you, too.

11:17.240 --> 11:18.840
A ship can't sail without its captain.

12:31.360 --> 12:38.280
NANWU

12:40.480 --> 12:42.360
The number you are dialing is powered off.

12:42.440 --> 12:43.720
Please try again later.

12:45.760 --> 12:47.160
Still no news?

12:50.880 --> 12:52.040
Thanks for your help.

12:52.720 --> 12:53.800
I appreciate it.

12:55.520 --> 12:57.280
Come on. Let's get lunch.

12:57.800 --> 12:59.440
There are still three meetings left.

13:02.480 --> 13:03.320
I'm not hungry.

13:05.520 --> 13:07.800
Since you're back at work now,
stop looking so gloomy.

13:09.280 --> 13:10.560
Even if you're upset,

13:10.640 --> 13:11.880
Wen Yifan won't come back.

13:13.720 --> 13:14.680
If you ask me,

13:14.760 --> 13:16.320
if Wen Yifan is really
in Hong Kong, China,

13:17.000 --> 13:19.480
she's either studying or working.

13:20.400 --> 13:22.240
She wouldn't just be hanging around

13:22.880 --> 13:25.080
and enjoying the view all day, right?

13:27.040 --> 13:29.520
Didn't your grandparents
live in Hong Kong, China, before?

13:30.040 --> 13:32.720
- Can you ask them to help look into it?
- Of course, no problem.

13:33.400 --> 13:36.760
But what if Xiang Lang
was just seeing things?

13:36.840 --> 13:38.240
Look at those thick glasses of his.

13:38.320 --> 13:39.600
He's definitely nearsighted.

13:39.680 --> 13:40.680
Maybe he mistook someone else for her.

13:42.040 --> 13:44.680
This time, I found the hotel
she once stayed at.

13:45.200 --> 13:47.480
The receptionist said a girl
from Nanwu stayed there before.

13:50.320 --> 13:52.200
Could it just be a coincidence?

13:54.640 --> 13:56.080
She said that the girl's surname…

13:57.080 --> 13:57.960
was Sang.

14:07.080 --> 14:08.240
I'm sorry.

14:08.320 --> 14:10.600
Still no news about Wen Yifan.

14:11.120 --> 14:14.280
Grandma, didn't you ask a few
of your old colleagues?

14:14.960 --> 14:16.560
You think my connections are so great

14:16.640 --> 14:18.240
that I know everyone in Hong Kong, China?

14:19.240 --> 14:21.800
But a few of my friends
in finance and education

14:21.880 --> 14:24.280
agreed to seriously help look for her.

14:25.520 --> 14:26.960
Grandma, thank you.

14:27.560 --> 14:29.360
Don't worry.

14:29.440 --> 14:30.760
If it's meant to be,

14:31.480 --> 14:33.000
just like those two,

14:33.080 --> 14:35.440
you'll find your way back together.

14:35.520 --> 14:36.800
Right, trust me.

14:36.880 --> 14:38.680
She was gone for so long before,

14:38.760 --> 14:40.000
but in the end, you still found her.

14:42.440 --> 14:43.880
I hope I get that lucky again.

14:43.960 --> 14:45.400
Kid,

14:45.480 --> 14:47.640
have you heard of the Law of Attraction?

14:47.720 --> 14:50.240
If your belief is strong enough,

14:50.320 --> 14:52.400
you'll get the result you want.

14:53.080 --> 14:54.560
I'm good at reading people.

14:54.640 --> 14:57.000
He doesn't seem like someone
who gives up easily.

14:57.080 --> 14:58.080
Am I right?

15:28.480 --> 15:29.640
Wendy,

15:29.720 --> 15:32.080
do those shoes fit you?

15:33.680 --> 15:35.120
- Those…
- Sen,

15:35.800 --> 15:38.640
- who is she?
- I'll explain later.

15:39.440 --> 15:41.080
- Are you two dating?
- I'll explain later.

15:44.160 --> 15:45.600
All of them…

15:45.680 --> 15:47.240
You've met before. They're a bit wild.

15:47.320 --> 15:49.680
So, if you have any problems,

15:49.760 --> 15:50.960
just come to me.

15:51.480 --> 15:52.800
Everybody,

15:52.880 --> 15:55.000
let me introduce your new instructor,

15:55.080 --> 15:56.040
Miss Wen.

15:56.120 --> 15:57.600
You can call her Wendy.

15:58.360 --> 15:59.320
Hello, Wendy!

16:00.800 --> 16:01.800
I remember you.

16:01.880 --> 16:03.440
How's your movement training going?

16:03.520 --> 16:05.040
I'm doing much better now!

16:05.120 --> 16:06.440
I'll check on it later.

16:06.520 --> 16:09.040
- And the rest of you?
- I'm Candy.

16:10.000 --> 16:11.160
I'm Bella.

16:11.240 --> 16:12.440
You're a Bella, too?

16:12.520 --> 16:13.480
Yes.

16:13.560 --> 16:14.840
Why are we switching teachers?

16:15.640 --> 16:18.160
Our previous teacher
had a family emergency.

16:18.240 --> 16:19.880
Wendy teaches really well!

16:19.960 --> 16:21.200
Say hello to Wendy.

16:21.280 --> 16:22.720
Hello, Wendy.

16:24.200 --> 16:25.760
Alright. I'm Wendy.

16:25.840 --> 16:29.320
From now on, I'll be teaching you ballet.
Is that okay?

16:30.000 --> 16:32.000
- Yes!
- Yes!

16:32.080 --> 16:34.120
Then, let's get ready

16:34.200 --> 16:35.400
and start class, okay?

16:35.480 --> 16:37.440
- Okay!
- Okay!

16:42.320 --> 16:43.360
Mom.

16:53.200 --> 16:54.720
When are you going to Hong Kong, China?

16:55.560 --> 16:56.920
The day after tomorrow, in the evening.

16:58.120 --> 16:59.120
Take this.

16:59.960 --> 17:01.840
Isn't this the gift
I gave you a few days ago?

17:01.920 --> 17:02.760
Why are you giving it back?

17:03.520 --> 17:05.280
Aren't you going with Haoan?

17:06.440 --> 17:07.520
Look at your skin.

17:08.400 --> 17:10.200
You're out in the sun and wind every day.

17:10.280 --> 17:11.960
Be mindful of aging.

17:12.680 --> 17:15.240
Make yourself look nice
when you go out with him.

17:15.319 --> 17:18.200
Maybe he'll fall for you even more.

17:18.280 --> 17:20.680
Mom, I don't care if he likes it or not.

17:20.760 --> 17:22.800
This is the real me.

17:22.880 --> 17:24.760
Besides, we're going to find Wen Yifan,

17:24.839 --> 17:25.720
not on some date.

17:26.480 --> 17:27.720
I know.

17:28.240 --> 17:29.680
You're so independent now.

17:30.200 --> 17:32.480
I don't even know how to help you anymore.

17:35.280 --> 17:36.600
I'm afraid I might
just be a burden to you.

17:37.440 --> 17:39.200
Mom, what are you saying?

17:39.280 --> 17:40.960
How could you be a burden to me?

17:42.000 --> 17:43.840
When it comes to relationships,
I have my own judgment.

17:43.920 --> 17:45.120
You don't have to worry about it.

17:48.120 --> 17:49.400
Alright.

17:51.560 --> 17:52.600
Fine.

17:53.280 --> 17:55.120
Come on. Let's do our skincare together.

18:04.400 --> 18:05.240
Qiao,

18:05.920 --> 18:08.520
what exactly are you unsure about Haoan?

18:09.480 --> 18:10.960
He's a great guy.

18:11.600 --> 18:12.680
And he treats me really well.

18:13.680 --> 18:14.800
Then, isn't that good?

18:16.760 --> 18:20.160
I just hope he can love me in a way

18:20.720 --> 18:22.640
that's different

18:23.160 --> 18:24.840
from his past relationships.

18:26.240 --> 18:27.600
What do you mean?

18:30.080 --> 18:31.200
I don't know.

18:31.720 --> 18:33.160
It's just a feeling.

18:33.680 --> 18:35.920
That's why I'm still waiting.

18:47.280 --> 18:48.560
Are you sure?

18:50.720 --> 18:52.360
Grandma's friend
is a professor at the university.

18:52.440 --> 18:53.880
He really found a graduate student

18:53.960 --> 18:55.080
named Wen Yifan.

18:55.160 --> 18:56.680
Plus, Xiang Lang has seen her before.

18:57.760 --> 18:59.840
And Sang Yan found
the hotel where she had stayed.

18:59.920 --> 19:01.480
These clues are pretty clear now.

19:02.480 --> 19:04.280
Are we really not going

19:05.000 --> 19:06.000
to tell Sang Yan?

19:06.880 --> 19:08.160
Last time,

19:08.680 --> 19:10.520
he was so disappointed when he came back.

19:10.600 --> 19:12.720
And besides, I'm worried
Wen Yifan will reject us again.

19:13.680 --> 19:15.200
Maybe we should go
and try talking to her first.

19:15.840 --> 19:16.920
Yeah.

19:17.000 --> 19:18.840
Dian is really stubborn.

19:18.920 --> 19:20.080
Even if we find her,

19:20.160 --> 19:22.520
convincing her to come back to Nanwu
won't be easy.

19:23.200 --> 19:24.720
If we don't find Wen Yifan,

19:24.800 --> 19:26.960
we'll be short a major
shareholder for Overtime.

19:27.560 --> 19:29.880
Maybe… I should sell my shares
to you at a discount,

19:29.960 --> 19:31.160
so you can take Sang Yan's place.

19:31.920 --> 19:33.200
Stop joking.

19:33.280 --> 19:35.240
Don't overthink it.

19:35.320 --> 19:36.400
Let's find her first.

19:51.800 --> 19:53.600
Hello. I have a reservation.

19:54.320 --> 19:56.000
Mr. Su, welcome back.

19:56.080 --> 19:57.640
Would you like one room?

19:58.560 --> 20:00.920
- Two.
- One room is fine.

20:02.800 --> 20:04.760
It's not like we've never
shared a bed before.

20:04.840 --> 20:06.160
What are you afraid of?

20:06.240 --> 20:08.040
I just think staying in the same room

20:08.120 --> 20:09.320
will make it easier to talk to Dian.

20:14.720 --> 20:15.920
Thank you.

20:17.520 --> 20:19.760
You seem pretty close
with the receptionist.

20:24.360 --> 20:25.360
No, not really.

20:26.880 --> 20:27.800
I just stay here

20:27.880 --> 20:31.080
whenever I help my grandparents
with things.

20:32.160 --> 20:34.600
Feels like you're a regular here.

20:34.680 --> 20:36.040
Have you been here
with Wang Linlin before?

20:36.120 --> 20:37.200
No.

20:39.200 --> 20:40.040
What about an ex?

20:41.040 --> 20:41.880
Or the ex before that?

20:42.560 --> 20:43.840
Or the one before that?

20:43.920 --> 20:45.720
My rule is,

20:46.320 --> 20:47.800
never go on trips with girlfriends.

20:51.000 --> 20:52.960
You have a rule for that?

20:55.760 --> 20:58.400
Traveling means spending all day together.

20:58.480 --> 21:01.160
If your values and habits don't match,

21:01.800 --> 21:03.600
you'll be arguing the whole time.

21:05.360 --> 21:06.560
And I also worry

21:06.640 --> 21:07.840
we'd break up
before the trip is even over.

21:07.920 --> 21:09.120
That'd be super awkward.

21:12.160 --> 21:13.200
But…

21:15.000 --> 21:16.960
I feel at ease when going out with you.

21:23.440 --> 21:25.680
Even though…

21:27.520 --> 21:30.560
relationship doesn't mean
you have to change for someone,

21:31.280 --> 21:32.200
I think…

21:34.120 --> 21:35.680
I really have changed.

21:37.680 --> 21:38.760
How so?

21:41.120 --> 21:42.000
Well…

21:42.680 --> 21:44.160
I feel like…

21:45.280 --> 21:47.320
I've become more relaxed.

21:48.080 --> 21:50.360
When I'm with you, I can say anything.

21:51.560 --> 21:53.280
I can laugh and cry.

21:55.560 --> 21:57.280
Life feels so much happier that way

21:57.880 --> 21:58.920
and so much more grounded.

22:00.400 --> 22:02.800
It's like I can tell you anything

22:02.880 --> 22:04.640
and share everything with you.

22:06.960 --> 22:10.240
But there's one thing

22:11.320 --> 22:12.480
that's a bit complicated.

22:17.680 --> 22:18.560
What is it?

22:28.640 --> 22:30.600
Right now, with you beside me,

22:32.120 --> 22:33.400
I feel like I'm burning up.

22:34.320 --> 22:36.120
I want to rush over,

22:36.200 --> 22:38.040
hold you in my arms,
and kiss you like crazy.

22:38.680 --> 22:41.680
But I'm trying so hard to control myself.

22:43.040 --> 22:45.040
I have to be honest…

22:46.480 --> 22:47.640
It's really tough.

23:05.760 --> 23:07.280
I want us to be together.

23:11.760 --> 23:13.520
I've been waiting so long
to hear you say that.

23:23.520 --> 23:24.760
Wait.

23:25.320 --> 23:28.000
Did you bring protection?

23:30.920 --> 23:33.200
How would I know I should plan ahead?

23:42.880 --> 23:43.920
Then…

23:44.520 --> 23:45.800
I'll buy some tomorrow.

23:53.080 --> 23:54.080
Let's sleep.

24:06.120 --> 24:08.000
Aren't you getting in?

24:09.360 --> 24:10.200
I am.

24:41.320 --> 24:44.360
LYCHEE YOGHURT DRINK

24:46.080 --> 24:48.160
You… can't sleep?

24:49.800 --> 24:52.120
You… can't either?

25:25.400 --> 25:29.520
Then… let's just stay here
and wait for the sunrise.

25:39.600 --> 25:40.520
So…

25:41.920 --> 25:44.240
Can we make it official on social media?

26:00.200 --> 26:01.040
Here.

26:01.920 --> 26:03.520
- Thanks.
- The school office is so annoying.

26:03.600 --> 26:05.200
They won't release student info

26:05.280 --> 26:06.640
because of privacy laws.

26:06.720 --> 26:08.600
Qiao, don't we have
a smarter way to do this?

26:08.680 --> 26:10.800
It's way too hot. Going around
asking one by one is not the way.

26:11.800 --> 26:13.360
Can't you be a little patient?

26:15.880 --> 26:17.840
Hello. Do you know Wen Yifan?

26:20.760 --> 26:24.520
Sorry. Do you know Wen Yifan?

26:24.600 --> 26:25.440
Sorry, I don't.

26:26.560 --> 26:27.400
Thank you.

26:28.120 --> 26:30.000
Hello. Do you know Wen Yifan?

26:30.560 --> 26:31.600
No, I don't.

26:35.320 --> 26:37.040
- Have you asked her?
- Alright.

26:37.120 --> 26:38.920
In just two weeks,

26:39.000 --> 26:40.960
we'll be performing on stage.
Are you nervous?

26:41.560 --> 26:42.920
- Yeah.
- If you're nervous,

26:43.000 --> 26:44.360
then we need to practice more.

26:44.440 --> 26:45.640
You're not nervous? Then,

26:46.680 --> 26:48.280
I'll demonstrate it again for you.

26:48.360 --> 26:49.520
Stand in fifth position.

26:50.560 --> 26:53.480
Remember, when you jump, cross
your feet in the air before landing.

26:53.560 --> 26:54.560
Okay?

26:54.640 --> 26:56.720
Hands up. Second position.

26:56.800 --> 26:59.680
Ready. One, two, three.

27:00.560 --> 27:03.280
Good. Now, let's try it again
with the left foot.

27:06.880 --> 27:08.320
Fifth position.

27:08.840 --> 27:11.080
One, two, three.

27:14.520 --> 27:15.480
Got it?

27:16.160 --> 27:19.600
Alright, show me one more time, okay?

27:20.480 --> 27:21.480
Come on.

27:25.920 --> 27:27.520
Is your foot okay?

27:28.360 --> 27:29.200
I'm fine.

27:30.040 --> 27:30.880
I can cover the lesson.

27:31.600 --> 27:33.280
It's okay. I'll be fine in a bit.

27:34.640 --> 27:35.520
Really?

27:38.880 --> 27:40.720
Molly, show me one more time, okay?

27:41.720 --> 27:42.760
Get ready.

27:43.800 --> 27:45.600
Three, two, one.

27:53.320 --> 27:55.920
Sen, you're so pragmatic.

27:56.000 --> 27:57.240
You only treat me to a meal

27:57.320 --> 27:59.440
when you're too shy to ask a girl out.

27:59.520 --> 28:01.280
You talk too much.

28:01.800 --> 28:04.080
Don't make things up.
I treat you to meals all the time.

28:04.600 --> 28:06.200
See? You admitted it yourself.

28:06.280 --> 28:07.320
How many dates have you been on?

28:07.400 --> 28:09.840
I should be the one treating you today.

28:09.920 --> 28:12.360
Thank you guys
for helping me reconnect with dance.

28:13.520 --> 28:14.560
No worries.

28:14.640 --> 28:16.440
Let's just call it a celebration
for your return to ballet.

28:18.800 --> 28:21.960
Yifan said that after her injury,
she stopped dancing.

28:22.040 --> 28:23.120
You even knew about that?

28:23.200 --> 28:25.200
No. You were late just now.

28:25.280 --> 28:26.920
We were chatting.

28:27.600 --> 28:30.200
Same here. I've lost count
of how many times I've broken my toes.

28:30.280 --> 28:31.800
That must've been rough.

28:33.680 --> 28:36.520
I'll have the coconut peach gum milk.

28:36.600 --> 28:38.920
It's great for recovery after an injury.

28:39.520 --> 28:40.520
I have it all the time.

28:41.040 --> 28:42.320
Thanks.

28:43.080 --> 28:45.440
Sweet. Really good.

28:46.320 --> 28:48.440
But in life, getting hurt is inevitable.

28:48.520 --> 28:50.120
You can get hurt dancing.

28:50.200 --> 28:51.480
You can get hurt cutting your hair.

28:51.560 --> 28:53.200
Even trimming your nails can go wrong.

28:54.440 --> 28:55.640
But it's okay.

28:56.520 --> 28:58.080
We recover after getting hurt.

28:58.720 --> 29:00.040
Then we get hurt again.

29:00.760 --> 29:02.840
Then we recover again.

29:04.000 --> 29:05.640
That's how we become unstoppable.

29:06.360 --> 29:08.040
Got it, Yuqing?

29:08.800 --> 29:11.600
More or less,
we'll all face setbacks, right?

29:11.680 --> 29:13.600
But life is fair.

29:14.280 --> 29:15.520
You'll have a hundred setbacks.

29:15.600 --> 29:16.920
You'll have a hundred setbacks.

29:17.000 --> 29:18.480
I'll have a hundred setbacks.

29:19.120 --> 29:20.440
But isn't it better to face them sooner

29:20.520 --> 29:22.240
rather than later? Right?

29:23.480 --> 29:25.000
Right? Right!

29:25.880 --> 29:28.520
So, I'm really happy now.

29:29.520 --> 29:31.880
Because I've already been through so much.

29:34.240 --> 29:35.120
Are you guys happy?

29:39.640 --> 29:40.480
Are you happy?

29:43.440 --> 29:44.720
Maybe.

29:45.560 --> 29:47.280
Have you had a lot of setbacks?

29:48.440 --> 29:50.240
You're really annoying.

29:50.320 --> 29:51.800
Fine. I'll eat.

29:51.880 --> 29:53.880
Thank you, Sen, for the lesson.

29:54.600 --> 29:55.880
Yifan, does it make sense?

30:06.840 --> 30:07.680
Check, please.

30:09.600 --> 30:12.440
Sen is such an optimist.

30:13.160 --> 30:16.480
He used to be a second-string dancer
at the New York City Ballet.

30:17.120 --> 30:20.440
I remember he was there
for about four years.

30:21.200 --> 30:22.080
He finally worked his way up

30:22.160 --> 30:24.080
to an opening in the first team.

30:24.160 --> 30:27.080
He was all set to perform
in Paris next month.

30:27.160 --> 30:28.800
But then, while celebrating

30:28.880 --> 30:30.760
with a steak he had just bought,

30:31.360 --> 30:34.120
a speeding car came right at him.

30:34.880 --> 30:36.400
And his leg…

30:37.640 --> 30:38.920
His dream was gone.

30:41.520 --> 30:43.160
He spent a long time recovering.

30:43.840 --> 30:45.600
You can imagine how painful it was.

30:47.440 --> 30:48.880
But that's just who he is,

30:49.560 --> 30:51.120
always optimistic, always upbeat,

30:51.640 --> 30:52.800
and always willing to help others.

30:53.680 --> 30:55.280
And guess what the first thing he said

30:55.360 --> 30:57.120
when he came back on crutches?

30:57.200 --> 30:58.240
He said,

30:59.200 --> 31:01.240
"It doesn't matter. I can still stay here

31:01.320 --> 31:03.640
in my beloved Hong Kong, China,
and do what I love the most."

31:04.240 --> 31:05.160
That's what he said.

31:07.480 --> 31:08.400
What were you talking about?

31:09.080 --> 31:09.920
- Talking behind my back?
- No.

31:10.000 --> 31:11.160
No one was badmouthing you.

31:11.240 --> 31:13.120
I was just saying you're optimistic.

31:13.200 --> 31:15.160
Look at your reaction.

31:15.240 --> 31:17.120
I'm starting to think
you really were badmouthing me.

31:17.200 --> 31:18.120
I swear I wasn't.

31:18.200 --> 31:19.160
But it's fine.

31:19.240 --> 31:20.560
I'm used to it.

31:22.280 --> 31:24.000
He said he's competing
in a ballet competition

31:24.080 --> 31:25.560
next month.

31:25.640 --> 31:26.480
Right.

31:27.520 --> 31:28.520
Talented people
are just built differently.

31:28.600 --> 31:30.040
There's prize money involved.

31:30.760 --> 31:31.920
People are realistic like that.

31:32.000 --> 31:33.760
They only join for the money.

31:44.040 --> 31:45.280
Look, Wen Yifan!

31:52.080 --> 31:53.800
- Dian!
- Go ahead.

31:53.880 --> 31:55.120
Dian!

31:58.360 --> 32:01.120
I missed you so much! Dian!

32:01.200 --> 32:02.640
You've lost weight again!

32:03.880 --> 32:04.880
Why are you here?

32:04.960 --> 32:05.960
Because of you, obviously.

32:06.040 --> 32:08.080
Tonight, we're staying up
all night talking.

32:08.680 --> 32:10.080
At your place or my hotel?

32:11.400 --> 32:13.480
I have to work tonight.

32:13.560 --> 32:15.080
Maybe tomorrow. How about it?

32:15.600 --> 32:16.440
Alright.

32:18.360 --> 32:19.880
How did you even find me?

32:20.640 --> 32:21.480
Thanks to him.

32:22.200 --> 32:23.240
Yeah, me.

32:30.760 --> 32:32.360
I missed you so much!

32:43.000 --> 32:44.520
Qiao, I booked the restaurant.

32:44.600 --> 32:46.040
I'll send you the location.

32:48.600 --> 32:50.560
Tomorrow, 1 p.m.

33:00.160 --> 33:02.800
In the end, they still found me.

33:46.880 --> 33:50.760
JULY 18TH

34:08.840 --> 34:13.040
QIAO, SANG YAN

34:17.400 --> 34:18.760
SANG YAN

34:18.840 --> 34:19.880
WEN SHUANGJIANG, I'M FURIOUS
I'M FURIOUS THAT YOU NEVER TOLD ME

34:19.960 --> 34:21.120
WHAT HAPPENED IN THOSE SIX YEARS

34:21.199 --> 34:22.719
I'M FURIOUS AT MYSELF FOR ONLY NOW
TRYING TO UNDERSTAND YOUR PAST

34:22.800 --> 34:23.960
WEN SHUANGJIANG
YOU ALWAYS TRY TO PROTECT EVERYONE ELSE

34:24.040 --> 34:25.199
TRUST ME, I CAN PROTECT YOU
LET'S TALK, OKAY?

34:34.000 --> 34:36.360
You little brat. Where have you
been hiding for the past six months?

34:36.960 --> 34:38.400
I'll follow you anywhere.

34:38.480 --> 34:39.840
I will go with you

34:39.920 --> 34:41.400
to the ends of the earth.

34:41.480 --> 34:43.159
I don't need to hide from you.

34:43.719 --> 34:46.120
I can tell you right now
that I'm in Hong Kong, China.

34:49.440 --> 34:50.480
Che Xingde,

34:51.840 --> 34:53.800
I will never be afraid of you again.

34:56.920 --> 34:58.720
I will make sure you pay for what you did.

35:03.640 --> 35:05.440
Just running away

35:05.520 --> 35:07.080
only hurts everyone in the end.

35:19.280 --> 35:20.440
Ugh, I'm exhausted.

35:21.360 --> 35:22.720
What are you doing?

35:22.800 --> 35:24.680
Recharging my skin.

35:28.320 --> 35:29.520
I already promised Sang Yan.

35:29.600 --> 35:31.880
If I find Wen Yifan,
I'll text him right away.

35:31.960 --> 35:33.040
Why won't you let me tell him?

35:33.120 --> 35:34.960
She left Sang Yan without a word.

35:35.040 --> 35:36.480
She must have her reasons.

35:36.560 --> 35:38.680
I have to find out where she stands first.

35:39.480 --> 35:42.000
Wouldn't it be faster

35:42.080 --> 35:44.400
to just let Sang Yan and Wen Yifan
talk it out themselves?

35:44.480 --> 35:45.680
But what if she met someone better

35:45.760 --> 35:47.320
during this time?

35:48.760 --> 35:49.720
I'm telling you,

35:49.800 --> 35:51.200
that's impossible.

35:52.360 --> 35:53.560
Dian has so much to offer.

35:53.640 --> 35:55.400
There must be tons of guys after her.
How is it impossible?

35:59.840 --> 36:01.240
Indeed.

36:01.320 --> 36:02.920
Sang Yan

36:03.000 --> 36:04.440
isn't much to look at.

36:05.000 --> 36:06.760
He's got a sharp tongue and a bad temper.

36:07.320 --> 36:08.920
For Wen Yifan to find someone

36:09.000 --> 36:11.080
better than him, that's way too easy.

36:12.520 --> 36:14.840
Even if she hasn't met someone better,

36:14.920 --> 36:17.080
she's been living in Hong Kong,
China, for a long time now.

36:17.160 --> 36:18.920
She's definitely been through a lot.

36:19.000 --> 36:21.480
How can you be so sure
her feelings haven't changed?

36:21.560 --> 36:24.720
What if she never planned
on getting back with Sang Yan?

36:24.800 --> 36:26.600
If they don't get back together,

36:26.680 --> 36:29.720
it'll take him years to get over it.

36:30.360 --> 36:33.440
So, let's hear
what Dian has to say tomorrow.

36:34.480 --> 36:35.520
Now, eat your noodles.

36:35.600 --> 36:36.800
Or they'll turn to mush.

36:42.200 --> 36:43.160
What's this?

36:46.080 --> 36:47.040
A sexy nightgown.

36:50.520 --> 36:52.480
Um… It's my mom's…

36:53.280 --> 36:54.320
I mean,

36:54.400 --> 36:56.600
it's my mom's sleepwear.

36:56.680 --> 36:59.520
I have no idea
how it ended up in my suitcase.

37:00.440 --> 37:01.320
Let's eat the noodles.

37:18.800 --> 37:20.640
How are we going
to bring this up with her?

37:21.160 --> 37:22.240
We can't

37:22.320 --> 37:23.760
just ask her outright
if she has a new boyfriend.

37:23.840 --> 37:24.680
She wouldn't tell us anyway.

37:28.240 --> 37:31.040
Why don't we ask her how life
in Hong Kong, China, has been?

37:31.640 --> 37:33.200
Let's start with something casual,

37:33.280 --> 37:35.440
then bring up the tougher questions.

37:35.520 --> 37:37.480
- How about that?
- Sounds good.

37:39.960 --> 37:41.920
What would you like? Check the menu.

37:43.520 --> 37:45.200
Dian!

37:46.280 --> 37:47.240
You can sit here.

37:48.200 --> 37:49.040
Thanks.

37:49.880 --> 37:51.000
Check the menu and see what you'd like.

37:52.080 --> 37:54.040
- Did you guys order yet?
- Not yet.

37:54.120 --> 37:55.840
I'm just so happy we found you.

37:55.920 --> 37:58.880
Can I tell Sang Yan where you are?

38:01.000 --> 38:03.280
Right. He's been searching
for you like crazy.

38:05.480 --> 38:06.800
I'll tell him myself.

38:14.720 --> 38:16.400
Alright, let's order.

38:17.000 --> 38:17.840
Okay.

38:18.560 --> 38:19.640
Then…

38:19.720 --> 38:21.040
- let's just order something for her.
- Yes.

38:21.120 --> 38:21.960
Fine.

38:53.760 --> 38:55.640
What do you think they're talking about?

38:56.400 --> 38:57.240
I have no idea.

38:59.880 --> 39:02.000
"Sang Yan, I want to break up."

39:02.080 --> 39:03.920
- Could that be it?
- No way.

39:05.120 --> 39:06.280
If she really dumps him…

39:08.600 --> 39:12.320
I'm afraid… Sang Yan will…
get even more bad-tempered.

39:13.400 --> 39:14.880
Stop jinxing it.

39:21.520 --> 39:22.360
Dian.

39:24.200 --> 39:25.680
Here you are.

39:27.840 --> 39:29.160
He's coming to Hong Kong, China.

39:51.640 --> 39:56.760
THE STORY IS NOT OVER YET…

40:35.840 --> 40:36.880
Sang Yan…

40:44.080 --> 40:45.360
How have you been?

40:50.240 --> 40:51.720
The guy who still owes me 20 bucks

40:53.520 --> 40:54.920
disappeared to who knows where.

40:57.600 --> 40:58.800
How could I sleep peacefully?

41:06.240 --> 41:07.840
Can we meet?

44:03.000 --> 44:03.840
HUGE THANKS TO EVERYONE INVOLVED
AND TO ALL THE FANS OF THE FIRST FROST!

44:03.920 --> 44:04.760
TREAT YOURSELF WELL
AND THE WORLD WILL HOLD MORE LOVE FOR YOU!
